title: Yksi suudelma
content_vision: The lyrics unfold the tale of a vintage summer, where old melodies blend with the sound of waves, creating a nostalgic yet fresh feel. It tells stories of past summer loves, sun-kissed memories, and the timeless charm of seaside adventures with a modern twist, emphasizing the sophisticated yet fun atmosphere the campaign desires.
